    redSet3Text2: `While health is their top priority, this group also includes a significant percentage of convenience and value seekers who prioritize time-saving and value-for-money options compared to other colors.`,
    greenSet1Text1: `<b>Globally, 45% of consumers find green-colored foods appealing.</b> Those attracted to green-colored foods are predominantly aged 25-44, with 33% in the 35-44 age group, indicating a stronger appeal within this range. Their food choices are strongly influenced by a health-conscious attitude, often favoring fresh, natural, and organic options. Additionally, 22% of this group are eco-conscious, further reinforcing their preference for environmentally friendly choices.`,
