    greenSet3Text2: `This group is particularly health-conscious, favoring fresh, natural, and organic options. They also prioritize affordability and seek good value for their money.  Additionally, they are meticulous about assessing the nutritional value of their food—such as calories, sugar levels, and vitamins—even more so than those who are attracted to green-colored foods and sauces.`,
